sets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb31de13c54f49c80d00a51e6c42046534d3772f","tid":15411,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"劣改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n<br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過"},{"pid":"f027426139ece33e3b1d2339f8fa56320a739298","tid":15411,"uid":30505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"聽緊隻歌個陣咁啱見到個post <br />\n無晒feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d33eb119ff9bf8147de8ca9cff59b2be57e92ee","tid":15411,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劣改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n</span><br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0995ff703b613459f9b915a229bcc20eadc7cad","tid":15411,"uid":32984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288629b0ad9b8ab422101c6ca46feb2c3c23fa6d","tid":15411,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽緊隻歌個陣咁啱見到個post <br />\n<br />\n無晒feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ee61332779f095b793f7a62762d7095a2c52a1","tid":15411,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劣改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何坐過那廁所板無故失蹤了<br />\n洗手間怎麼這麼快沒廁所水<br />\n為何每次你要抆屎還有幾千格<br />\n轉手到我竟找不到廁紙<br />\n<br />\n也許這刻你　仍然尚未發覺<br />\n出公廁屙得更寫意<br />\n時時漏夜撞入女廁<br />\n將一打M巾帶走　循環做廁紙<br />\n<br />\n在你的數簿放低廁板是我<br />\n算是暗中　Claim幾千蚊去出火<br />\n從你的廁所帶走馬桶是我<br />\n你坐過的　至少我都坐過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a072dc6e10560dae